## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **suzetrigine Journavx 2024** = first FDA Nav1.8 selective. acute pain 적응증 first; chronic neuropathic Phase 3 development 진행. opioid 대체 paradigm shift first credible non-opioid Nav1.8. quantum-VQE 의 Nav1.8 pocket selectivity (vs Nav1.5 cardiac) 가 직접 fit.
2. **pregabalin Lyrica 2004** = first FDA DPN + PHN + fibromyalgia α2δ. gabapentin precedent + 1L expansion. 20+ years 임상 stable. quantum-VQE 의 α2δ-1 vs α2δ-2 selectivity 가 falls 부작용 source.
3. **duloxetine Cymbalta 2004** = first FDA DPN + PHN + fibromyalgia + chronic musculoskeletal SNRI. SNRI multi-indication broad. quantum-VQE 의 SERT/NET dual binding pocket.
4. **capsaicin 8% Qutenza 2009** = first FDA TRPV1 patch — PHN + DPN. high-concentration single-application paradigm. quantum-VQE 의 TRPV1 vanilloid pocket.
5. **ziconotide Prialt 2004** = N-type Ca channel intrathecal — synthetic ω-conotoxin MVIIA. 만성 refractory pain 마지막 옵션. quantum-VQE 의 peptide + N-type pocket.
6. **vutrisiran 2022 + patisiran 2018** = TTR siRNA — 만성 ATTR neuropathy disease-modifying. RIBOZYME axis 직접 fit. cross-iag inherited adult.
7. **carbamazepine + oxcarbazepine** = first-line TN — HLA-B*1502 stevens-johnson/TEN pharmacogenomics. K-chronic pain framework + 식약처 PGx mandatory cross-link.
8. **nabiximols Sativex EU/한국 (US 미승인)** = THC + CBD oromucosal — MS spasticity + neuropathic. 美 FDA 미승인 + EU/한국/캐나다 승인 = regulatory geography divergence.
9. **vixotrigine Phase 3 TN** = Nav1.7 selective — TN Phase 3 ongoing. Nav1.7 selectivity 가 SCN9A loss-of-function CIP precedent. quantum-VQE 의 Nav1.7 vs Nav1.8 vs Nav1.5 selectivity grid.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, chronic neuropathic 임상 의미 한정. K-chronic pain + 산정특례 framework + 식약처 PGx 의 한국 정책 layer 가 추가 falsifier.

